<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Rothenburg ob der Tauber und Windsheim</head><p>Der Rat teilt im Geheimen mit, wegen der Judenschaft zu Nürnberg eine Gesandtschaft zu König Sigismund zu schicken aus Sorge, wieder belangt zu werden.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_464" id="231r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_464_r1l25"><expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> vnd winſheim <expan>yed<ex>er</ex></expan> ſtat <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_464_r1l26"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> von <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>anlangu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> proceſſ vnd mandat <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l27"><expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn vnd ʒu vns auch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> warn als von der <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l28"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſtette<ex>n</ex></expan> etc . Nu wıe wol <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſache bey vns noch ſteen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l29">vnd geſtalt ſeyn als do eẅr erber <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>nehſte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> bey vns was . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l30">Doch wan wır <expan>beſorge<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wır <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> angelangt <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_465" id="231v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_465_r1l1">ſo <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır auf heẅt <expan>beſloſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> erber <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_465_r1l2"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> etc künıg . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒutun / dıe ſıch auch in kürcʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_465_r1l3">bey vns <expan>erhebe<ex>n</ex></expan> wırdt . Das tun wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>ſunder<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_465_r1l4"><expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd geheim alſo ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / auf das ob Jr bedacht <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> not = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_465_r1l5">dürftıg weͣrt . eẅr erber <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch dahin ʒutun . daʒ Jr eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_465_r1l6">denn darnach weſt ʒu rıchten / vnd wellet dıe ſache alſo rats weıſe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_465_r1l7"><expan>behalte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Denn wo vvır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_465_r1l8"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_464" id="231r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und Winsheim,
                            <expan>yed<ex>er</ex></expan> stat
                            <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, von <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>anlangu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>, process und mandat
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn und zu uns auch
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> warn als von der
                                <expan>jüdisch<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>stette<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., nu wie wol
                            <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> sache bey uns noch steen und gestalt
                        seyn, als do ewr erber <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>nehste<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> bey uns was, doch wan wir
                                <expan>besorge<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> angelangt <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, <pb facs="#facs_465" id="231v"/>so
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir auf hewt
                            <expan>beslosse<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> erber
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                        künig <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu tun, die sich auch in kürcz bey uns
                                <expan>erhebe<ex>n</ex></expan> wirdt. Das tun wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>sunder<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und geheim also zu
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, auf das ob ir bedacht
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> notdürftig weͣrt, ewr erber
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch dahin zutun, daz ir ewch denn darnach
                        west zu richten, und wellet die sache also ratsweise
                                <expan>behalte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
